---
title: Chermoula Beef & Chickpea-Stuffed Capsicum with Leafy Couscous & Garlic Yoghurt
description: If you’re as crazy about capsicums as we are then gather around and try out the latest capsicum creation - they’re stuffed full of saucy beef & chickpeas beans sprinkled in Cheddar cheese to add a melted gooey layer on top. We’re these stuffed capsicum’s number one fans!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
